data.title: Repro of 1980's WVAH-TV Color Test Pattern
data.meta_description: A repro (with color film chain calibration approximation to match) of the test pattern of WVAH-TV Channel 23 in Charleston/Huntington, WV, from its early years on the air.  Based on what was seen on a TV DX site.  (The station is today a Fox affiliate on Channel 11.)
